description: doc: fix typo in laws of reflection article

messages.text:
Hello golang-dev@googlegroups.com,

I'd like you to review this change to
https://code.google.com/p/go/

This changes the pattern to look for doc/progs/interface.go but that
pattern does not appear to be there. I do see that the variable name is
inconsistent with the text on the next line. If the goal is to change the
variable name to 'e' to match the text, you should also include in this CL
a change to doc/progs/interface.go.

I fixed the issue in a separate CL.

-rob
